{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, aligned visual features can be considered a special case of soft prompts -visually conditioned soft prompts -sharing the characteristic of residing in a representation space distinct from the language embedding space.",
    "• ChatGPT: Sorry, I don't see the arrow in the image.",
    "• Claude: A sleek fish glides through the harbor waters, its scales catching glints of sunlight filtering through the surface.",
    "The backdrop features wooden pier posts rising from the water and moored fishing boats gently bobbing in the distance.",
    "The water has a deep blue-green tint typical of a working harbor, with small ripples creating patterns of light and shadow."
  ]
}